{
  "$comment": "Per-phase model preference for loom-sdlc panels. Panel shape is enforced by each phase's min_panel: the resolver dedupes to one model per vendor, so min_panel is the distinct-vendor floor; plus rules.exclude_author_vendor. This file expresses preference; resolve-panel.sh reconciles it against live credentials. Model ids drift: re-check with dispatch-subagents/scripts/list-models.sh.",
